WEBVTT

00:06:27.744 --> 00:06:31.313
which is, how do you set up for wisdom?

00:06:31.313 --> 00:06:35.989
We've come from an age of revolution,
industrial revolution,

00:06:35.989 --> 00:06:38.672
an age of information,
an age of knowledge,

00:06:38.672 --> 00:06:41.284
but we're not any closer
to the age of wisdom.

00:06:41.284 --> 00:06:44.611
How we design, how do we organize,
for more wisdom?

00:06:44.611 --> 00:06:46.154
So for example, many times,

00:06:46.154 --> 00:06:50.501
what's the smartest or the intelligent
decision doesn't jive.

00:06:50.501 --> 00:06:52.883
So we'd say things like,

00:06:52.883 --> 00:06:56.890
let's agree that you're going to sell
57 widgets per week.

00:06:56.890 --> 00:07:00.563
If you sell them by Wednesday, 
please go to the beach.